===Pronoun===
'''[[one]] [[another]]'''

#{{idiom}} Used of a [[reciprocal]] [[relationship]] among a group of more than [[two]] people or things; compare [[each other]].
#* The raw recruits helped '''one another''' get over the first few days.
#* Rainy days seemed to follow '''one another''' all summer.

